          "docs": "Fetch a list of all 301 redirect rules configured for a specific site.\n\nUse this endpoint to review, audit, or manage the redirection rules that control how traffic is rerouted on your site.\n\n<Warning title=\"Enterprise Only\">This endpoint requires an Enterprise workspace.</Warning>\n\nRequired scope: `sites:read`\n"
        },
        {
          "info": {
            "name": "Webflow Create a 301 redirect",
            "type": "http"
